    "date": "2004-09-08T16:00:02Z",
    "text": "Zero Downpayment Act of 2004 - Amends the National Housing Act to authorize the Secretary of Housing and Urban Development to insure zero-downpayment mortgages of an eligible single family residence for a first-time homebuyer who has received specified homeownership counseling.\n\nTerminates program authority after September 30, 2011, except for mortgages executed prior to such date."
